'''ITV格拉納達'''（'''{{lang-en|ITV Granada}}'''），舊名'''格拉納達電視'''（Granada Television），是[[西北英格蘭|西北英格蘭]]的[[獨立電視網|獨立電視網]]（ITV）特許經營權持有者。在1956年至1968年，其還持有[[約克郡|約克郡]]地區的獨立電視網特許經營權，但播出時段僅限週一至週五（週末的ITV特許經營權業者是[[ABC週末電視|ABC週末電視]]）。格拉納達電視的母公司[[格拉納達股份|格拉納達股份]]在1990年代後收購了多家其它ITV特許經營權業者，並在2004年和[[卡爾頓通信股份|卡爾頓通信股份]]合併成為[[獨立電視公司|獨立電視公司]]。現在西北英格蘭的[[獨立電視台_(英國)|獨立電視台]]使用「ITV」名稱播出，但「格拉納達」一名仍在地方新聞節目名得到延續。

在和卡爾頓合併之前，格拉納達是獨立電視網最大的節目供應商，佔ITV節目總量的25%。格拉納達也是1954年最初從{{link-en|獨立電視局|Independent Television Authority}}（ITA）獲得特許經營權的四家業者中唯一存在至今的業者。其播出地區包括[[柴郡|柴郡]]、[[大曼徹斯特|大曼徹斯特]]、[[蘭開夏郡|蘭開夏郡]]、[[默西賽德郡|默西賽德郡]]，以及[[德比郡|德比郡]]、[[坎布里亞|坎布里亞]]、[[北約克郡|北約克郡]]、[[北威爾斯|北威爾斯]]的部分地區<ref>{{cite web | url = http://www.itv.com/local/ | title = Your local news and weather | publisher = ITV | access-date = 2021-06-21 | archive-date = 2012-03-19 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20120319121753/http://www.itv.com/local/ | dead-url = no }}</ref> 。2009年，[[曼島|曼島]]從[[ITV國界|ITV國界]]改為格拉納達的播出地區。

格拉納達開播於1956年5月3日，是第五家開播的ITV特許經營權業者。其標誌融合了字母「G」和一個朝北的箭頭，並經常配以標語「格拉納達：來自北方（Granada: from the North）」<ref name="clark">{{Cite news |title=London calling |author=Liddiment, David |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/nov/24/mondaymediasection.northsouthdivide |work=The Guardian |location=London |date=2003-11-24 |access-date=2011-06-20 |archive-date=2020-03-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200310163139/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/nov/24/mondaymediasection.northsouthdivide |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

格拉納達被認為是ITV最為成功的業者<ref name="andthen">{{Cite news |title=And then there were three |last=Brown |first=Maggie |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2000/jul/17/mondaymediasection.towardsasingleitv |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2000-07-17 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925211951/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2000/jul/17/mondaymediasection.towardsasingleitv |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Obituary – David Plowright |quote=As he himself liked to quote, not for nothing had Granada been dubbed the best commercial television company in the world. |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/david-plowright-413771.html |newspaper=The Independent |date=2006-08-29 |access-date=2012-02-04 |archive-date=2012-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130161610/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/david-plowright-413771.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Party People returns as presenter Rob McLoughlin celebrates thirtieth year at ITV |quote=The Financial Times was to claim that 'Granada was probably the best commercial TV company in the world' – with respect to Thames TV; LWT and our American cousins –  they may have been right but when that quote was hauled over reception in Quay Street I found it both inspiring and daunting. |url=http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-features/special-features/party-people-returns-as-presenter-rob-mcloughlin-celebrates-thirtieth-year-at-itv-201 |date=2012-01-25 |access-date=2012-02-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120419172834/http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-features/special-features/party-people-returns-as-presenter-rob-mcloughlin-celebrates-thirtieth-year-at-itv-201 |archive-date=2012-04-19 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。2000年，有九個格拉納達的節目被列入{{link-en|BFI TV 100|BFI TV 100}}。格拉納達最著名的節目包括《[[歇洛克·福尔摩斯_(1984年电视剧)|福爾摩斯探案]]》、《[[加冕街|加冕街]]》、《[[成長系列|成長系列]]》、《{{link-en|皇室家庭|The Royle Family}}》、《{{link-en|皇冠上的寶石|The Jewel in the Crown (TV series)}}》、《[[故園風雨後|故園風雨後]]》、《{{link-en|世界在行動|World in Action}}》、《{{link-en|大學挑戰|University Challenge}}》、《{{link-en|The Krypton Factor|The Krypton Factor}}》。格拉納達電視的著名員工有[[保羅·葛林葛瑞斯|保羅·葛林葛瑞斯]]、[[迈克尔·艾普特|迈克尔·艾普特]]、[[迈克·纽维尔|迈克·纽维尔]]、{{link-en|傑瑞米·伊薩克斯|Jeremy Isaacs}}、{{link-en|安迪·哈利斯|Andy Harries}}、[[拉塞爾·T·戴維斯|拉塞爾·T·戴維斯]]、{{link-en|萊斯利·伍德希德|Leslie Woodhead}}、{{link-en|托尼·威爾森|Tony Wilson}}、{{link-en|丹·沃克|Dan Walker (broadcaster)}}。

==歷史==
===起源===
[[File:Granada_Television_until_1968_coverage_map.svg|thumb]]
格拉納達起源於南英格蘭的[[電影院|電影院]]公司格拉納達影院（Granada Theatres Ltd）。這家公司在1930年由西德尼·伯恩斯坦（Sidney Bernstein）和塞西爾·伯恩斯坦（Cecil Bernstein）兄弟創業於[[多佛|多佛]]。公司名取自於西班牙[[格拉納達|同名城市]]，西德尼曾到此旅行<ref>{{Cite news|last=Feddy|first=Kevin|date=15 February 2007|title=Sidney Bernstein|newspaper=Manchester Evening News|url=https://www.manchestereveningnews.co.uk/news/business/s/210383_sidney_bernstein|access-date=2020-12-03|quote=... named after the Spanish city where he had been on holiday.}}</ref>。格拉納達影院在1934年更名為格拉納達公司（Granada Ltd），並於翌年在[[倫敦證券交易所|倫敦證券交易所]]上市。格拉納達影院成為新公司的子公司<ref name=history>{{cite web|url=http://www.itvplc.com/about/history/|title=About ITV: History: March 2017|website=www.itvplc.com|access-date=2021-06-21|archive-date=2017-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170319194544/http://www.itvplc.com/about/history|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

1950年代，伯恩斯坦開始涉足商業電視行業，並贏得北英格蘭的ITV特許經營權（因為這樣不會影響公司在南部的影院生意）
{{Quote|text=北部和倫敦是兩個最大的地區。因其文化傳統，格拉納達更偏好北方。北方亦提供在遠離倫敦大都市氣氛開啟新的創意產業的機會；北方是一個緊密的、本土的工業社會；在音樂、戲劇、文學、報業都有卓越的同質文化群體。而這在英國其它地方都難以發現（蘇格蘭可能是個例外）。如果你看到北方的人口密度地圖和降水量地圖，你會發現北方是一個理想的發展電視業的場所。|sign=西德尼·伯恩斯坦在1954年決定在曼徹斯特開設格拉納達電視台的理由<ref name="sidneyb">{{cite web |title=Bernstein, Sidney |last=Pearson |first=Tony |url=http://www.museum.tv/archives/etv/B/htmlB/bernsteinsi/bersteinsi.htm |work=Museum of Broadcast Communications |access-date=2021-06-21 |archive-date=2002-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20020820142750/http://www.museum.tv/archives/etv/B/htmlB/bernsteinsi/bersteinsi.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>}}

伯恩斯坦考慮在利茲或曼徹斯特設立電視台總部，並最後以8.2萬英鎊的價格購買位於[[曼徹斯特市中心|曼徹斯特市中心]]的{{link-en|碼頭街|Quay Street}}的一片土地用來修建總部<ref name="founder">{{Cite news |title=Granada's Founding Father |url=http://www.teletronic.co.uk/bernstein.htm |work=teletronic.co.uk |access-date=2011-07-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110728065646/http://www.teletronic.co.uk/bernstein.htm |archive-date=2011-07-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。開播當晚的節目《Meet The People》由{{link-en|昆汀·雷諾茲|Quentin Reynolds}}和{{link-en|阿瑟·阿斯基|Arthur Askey}}主持<ref>{{Cite news |title=Meet The People – Launch Night from 1956 |url=http://www.tv-ark.org.uk/mivana/mediaplayer.php?id=75472a8f888434fb0ddd1b3abd8b84b1&media=granada_open&type=mp4 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110927004132/http://www.tv-ark.org.uk/mivana/mediaplayer.php?id=75472a8f888434fb0ddd1b3abd8b84b1&media=granada_open&type=mp4 |archive-date=2011-09-27 |work=tv-ark.org.uk |access-date=2011-07-27 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===早期歷史===
大多數ITV特許經營商都視其播出區域是贏得倫敦特許經營權之前的墊腳石。與之相反，格拉納達決定發展其北方特徵，並以「格拉納達來自北方（Granada from the north）」、「來自北方—格拉納達（From the north—Granada）」、「格拉納達蘭（Granadaland）」作為宣傳標語<ref>{{Cite news |title=ITV |quote=The North-West was sometimes known as 'Granadaland' |url=http://www.screenonline.org.uk/tv/id/1139047/index.html |work=British Film Institute |access-date=2011-08-05 |archive-date=2021-05-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210519220154/http://www.screenonline.org.uk/tv/id/1139047/index.html }}</ref>。伯恩斯坦無意僱傭任何拒絕搬家至曼徹斯特的人，傑瑞米·伊薩克斯因此稱他為「和藹的暴君」<ref>{{Cite news |title=Bernstein – genial tyrant of Granada: Jeremy Isaacs recalls his former boss and founder of the Granada group, who died at 94 |last=Isaacs |first=Jeremy |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/bernstein--genial-tyrant-of-granada-jeremy-isaacs-recalls-his-former-boss-and-founder-of-the-granada-group-who-died-at-94-1471579.html |newspaper=The Independent |date=1993-02-07 |access-date=2011-07-01 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925155227/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/uk/bernstein--genial-tyrant-of-granada-jeremy-isaacs-recalls-his-former-boss-and-founder-of-the-granada-group-who-died-at-94-1471579.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

{{Quote|text=我認為曼徹斯特現在看到的，倫敦最終也會看到。|sign=1950年代，西德尼·伯恩斯坦希望格拉納達最終成為英國廣播業的關鍵角色<ref name="friends">{{Cite news |title=Our friends in the north |last=Cooke |first=Rachel |url=http://www.newstatesman.com/television/2010/01/television-room-granada-urbis |work=New Statesman |location=London |date=2009-12-30 |access-date=2011-06-30 |archive-date=2021-01-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210123043342/https://www.newstatesman.com/television/2010/01/television-room-granada-urbis |dead-url=no }}</ref>。}}

伯恩斯坦決定修建新的攝影棚，而非租用建築或改造舊建築（這是其它ITV公司和BBC在曼徹斯特的做法）。1954年，對新攝影棚的投資導致格拉納達陷入財務困境。1956年末，格拉納達已瀕臨破產。最初的四家ITV業者都被認為將在最初數年虧損，但格拉納達的虧損高達17.5萬英鎊<ref name="moneywoes">{{Cite news|title = Granada Television|url = http://www.screenonline.org.uk/tv/id/507673/|publisher = British Film Institute|website = Screenonline|first = Richard G.|last = Elen|accessdate = 2021-06-21|archive-date = 2020-10-20|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201020092850/http://www.screenonline.org.uk/tv/id/507673/|dead-url = no}}</ref>（相當於2011年的近350萬英鎊）<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.bankofengland.co.uk/education/Pages/inflation/calculator/flash/default.aspx |title=Archived copy |access-date=2014-02-05 |archive-url=https://www.webcitation.org/6NA5SosVg?url=http://www.bankofengland.co.uk/education/Pages/inflation/calculator/flash/default.aspx |archive-date=2014-02-05 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在其第一次盈利時，格拉納達的盈利額是四家業者中最少的<ref name="moneywoes"/><ref name=patterson>{{cite book |author= Patterson, Richard |chapter=The Production Context of Coronation Street |title=Television Monograph: Coronation Street |url= https://archive.org/details/coronationstreet0000unse_t6y5 |year=1981 |isbn=0-85170-110-8 |publisher=British Film Institute |location=London |pages=[https://archive.org/details/coronationstreet0000unse_t6y5/page/54 54]–5}}</ref>。

格拉納達尋求倫敦平日ITV業者[[聯合-麗的|聯合-麗的]]的幫助，後者同意負擔格拉納達的部分債務；作為交換，聯合-麗的可獲得格拉納達部分利潤。格拉納達接受了這一條件。隨著ITV人氣提高，格拉納達的盈利能力也隨之增加<ref name="ReferenceA">{{cite book | author = Black, Peter | title = The mirror in the corner: People's television | url = https://archive.org/details/mirrorincornerpe0000blac | publisher = Hutchinson | location = London | year = 1972 | isbn = 978-0-09-110100-8}}</ref>。分析師曾質疑為何聯合-麗的、ABC和[[聯合電視|ATV]]在1959年賺取270萬英鎊利潤，而格拉納達的利潤不足100萬英鎊。隨著利潤增加，格拉納達試圖重新談判合同，但被聯合-麗的拒絕，導致兩者關係惡化。這一交易為麗的帶來超過800萬英鎊的利益<ref name="ReferenceA"/>。1960年代早期，格拉納達的肥皂劇《[[加冕街|加冕街]]》大受歡迎<ref name= "moneywoes"/>，其廉價的遊戲節目，如《{{link-en|Criss Cross Quiz|Criss Cross Quiz}}》和《{{link-en|大學挑戰|University Challenge}}》亦取得成功<ref>{{Cite news |title=Good programmes came first |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2006/oct/13/ITV.broadcasting?INTCMP=SRCH |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2006-10-13 |first=Jason |last=Deans |accessdate=2021-06-21 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925195253/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2006/oct/13/ITV.broadcasting?INTCMP=SRCH |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===特許經營權變更===
在1968年的ITV特許經營權變更中，格拉納達的播出範圍從北英格蘭改為西北英格蘭，約克郡成為一個單獨的特許經營權地區，由[[ITV約克郡|約克郡電視]]播出；但格拉納達的播出時間從週一至週五改為全週。伯恩斯坦對這一決定十分憤怒，並聲稱將會上訴<ref>{{harvnb|Forman|1997|p=195}}</ref>。

格拉納達在1980年的特許經營權審查中維持了其特許，並投資數百萬英鎊用於製作電視劇，《{{link-en|皇冠上的寶石|The Jewel in the Crown (TV series)}}》、《[[故園風雨後|故園風雨後]]》都是這一時期的作品<ref>{{Cite news |title=What is the outlook for ITV? |last=Douglas |first=Torin |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/7921427.stm |work=BBC News |date=2009-03-04 |access-date=2011-06-26}}</ref>。1980年代後期，英國的商業廣播公司被認為規模太小而無法在世界市場上競爭，ITV公司之間開始合併，目標是形成一家更大的公司<ref>{{Cite news |title=Now the talk is of one ITV |url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/1999/nov/27/15 |newspaper=The Guardian |quote=Mr Green said consolidation of ITV into one company was needed because the companies had to be in a position to compete with large overseas groups. |date=1999-11-27 |access-date=2011-08-01 |first=Chris |last=Barrie |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926194415/https://www.theguardian.com/business/1999/nov/27/15 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《1990年廣播法》的實施引發了1991年ITV特許經營權競標。{{link-en|萊姆影業|Lime Pictures|默西電視}}（[[第四台_(英國)|英國第四台]]肥皂劇《[[布魯克賽德|布魯克賽德]]》的製作公司）出價3,500萬英鎊，和格拉納達（出價900萬英鎊）競爭西北英格蘭的ITV特許經營權<ref name="plowright">{{Cite news |title=David Plowright |url=http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/obituaries/article621040.ece |newspaper=The Times |date=2006-08-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110622073858/http://www.timesonline.co.uk/tol/comment/obituaries/article621040.ece |archive-date=2011-06-22 |accessdate=2021-06-21 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但因默西電視未通過{{link-en|獨立電視委員會|Independent Television Commission}}規定的「品質門檻」，格拉納達順利維持特許經營權。格拉納達曾威脅稱如果失去特許經營權，將進軍[[衛星電視|衛星電視]]<ref name="plowright"/>。

自1957年開始為格拉納達服務的{{link-en|大衛·普勞萊特|David Plowright}}在1992年辭職，理由是{{link-en|蓋瑞·羅賓遜|Gerry Robinson}}的到來。後者以強硬方式緊縮預算<ref>{{Cite news |title=Why don't you please, Gerry Robinson? |last=Sylvester |first=Rachel |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/why-dont-you-please-gerry-robinson-1178933.html |newspaper=The Independent |date=1998-10-18 |access-date=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304065930/http://www.independent.co.uk/arts-entertainment/why-dont-you-please-gerry-robinson-1178933.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。普勞萊特一直是格拉納達的重要人物，製作了《{{link-en|世界在行動|World in Action}}》、《[[加冕街|加冕街]]》等著名節目，並推廣了{{link-en|格拉納達攝影棚之旅|Granada Studios Tour}}<ref>{{harvnb|Fitzwalter|2008|p=31}}</ref>。他的離開激怒了媒體業大佬：[[約翰·克里斯|約翰·克里斯]]給羅賓遜發了一封傳真，稱他是「暴發戶餐飲業者」（羅賓遜之前的工作）<ref>{{Cite news |title=David Plowright (obituary) |url= http://news.scotsman.com/obituaries/David-Plowright.2806062.jp |work=The Scotsman |location =Edinburgh |date=2006-08-29 |access-date=2011-06-28}}</ref>。{{link-en|約翰·伯特|John Birt}}、[[哈羅德·品特|哈羅德·品特]]和[[阿倫·班尼特|阿倫·班尼特]]都公開支持普勞萊特<ref>{{Cite news |title=David Plowright: Old-guard chairman of Granada who championed quality programming in commercial television |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/david-plowright-413771.html |newspaper=The Independent |location=London |author=Granger, Derek |date=2006-08-29 |access-date=2011-06-28 |archive-date=2012-01-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120130161610/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/obituaries/david-plowright-413771.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===併購===
業界預估ITV「五巨頭」（[[泰晤士電視|泰晤士]]、[[倫敦週末電視|LWT]], [[ITV中部|中部]]、格拉納達、約克郡）將併購另外十家規模較小的ITV特許經營商。格拉納達希望能和約克郡及[[ITV泰恩提茲|泰恩提茲]]合併，以「對抗東南部潛在的統治地位」<ref name="Fitzwalter">{{harvnb|Fitzwalter|2008|p=130}}</ref>，以及可能被泰晤士併購。1993年12月，格拉納達對LWT發起敵對性併購。LWT認為格拉納達雖然市值是其三倍，但並不能提供太多好處<ref name="lwtforeign">{{Cite news |title=LWT may seek foreign buyer to stop Granada: French group is a possible white knight |last=Counsell |first=Gail |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/lwt-may-seek-foreign-buyer-to-stop-granada-french-group-is-a-possible-white-knight--poison-pill-acquisition-is-ruled-out-1465976.html |newspaper=The Independent |location=London |date=1993-12-07 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925064707/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/lwt-may-seek-foreign-buyer-to-stop-granada-french-group-is-a-possible-white-knight--poison-pill-acquisition-is-ruled-out-1465976.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。格拉納達最後在1994年完成併購<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada wins bitter battle to own LWT: Chairman regrets loss of independence |last=Counsell |first=Gail |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/granada-wins-bitter-battle-to-own-lwt-chairman-regrets-loss-of-independence-1396543.html |newspaper=The Independent |location=London |date=1994-02-26 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-date=2019-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101174310/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/granada-wins-bitter-battle-to-own-lwt-chairman-regrets-loss-of-independence-1396543.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此後格拉納達繼續擴張，在1997年以6.52億英鎊的價格併購{{link-en|約克郡-泰恩提茲電視|Yorkshire-Tyne Tees Television}}<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada set to buy Yorkshire for pounds 652m |last=Newman |first=Cathy |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/granada-set-to-buy-yorkshire-for-pounds-652m-1255215.html |newspaper=The Independent |date=1997-06-10 |access-date=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2016-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820125314/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/business/granada-set-to-buy-yorkshire-for-pounds-652m-1255215.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；在2000年以1.75億英鎊的價格併購{{link-en|UBM公司|UBM plc|UNM}}的電視部門（包括[[ITV盎格利亞|盎格利亞]]、[[ITV子午線|子午線]]，以及[[ITV威爾士和西部|HTV]]的部分部門）<ref>{{Cite news |title=Hollick's TV empire is sold in a 'friendly' deal |last=McIntosh |first=Bill |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/hollicks-tv-empire-is-sold-in-a-friendly-deal-707384.html |newspaper=The Independent |date=2000-07-29 |access-date=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2016-08-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160820153957/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/media/hollicks-tv-empire-is-sold-in-a-friendly-deal-707384.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="BBCnews itv shake up">{{cite news|title=ITV shake-up continues|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/988003.stm|access-date=2011-10-27|newspaper=BBC News|date=2000-10-24|archive-date=2004-06-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040613030955/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/988003.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>。一年後，格拉納達收購了國界電視。2002年時，英格蘭和威爾斯的全部ITV業者均由格拉納達或[[卡爾頓通信股份|卡爾頓]]所有。

格拉納達財務狀況欠佳，並在2001年以遊客減少為由停止格拉納達攝影棚之旅<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada shuts tourist attraction |last=Rogers |first=Daniel |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2001/jan/18/broadcasting7?INTCMP=SRCH |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2001-01-18 |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925194945/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2001/jan/18/broadcasting7?INTCMP=SRCH |dead-url=no }}</ref>，並且還關閉了格拉納達電影<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada closes film wing |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2002/sep/11/broadcasting?INTCMP=SRCH |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2002-09-11 |access-date=2011-07-02 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926194807/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2002/sep/11/broadcasting?INTCMP=SRCH |dead-url=no }}</ref>。數位電視的出現降低了ITV的收視率，而和網路的競爭則減少了廣告收入<ref>{{Cite news |title=ITV loses 'licence to print money' |last=Douglas |first=Torin |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/1407543.stm |work=BBC |date=2001-06-25 |access-date=2011-07-03 |archive-date=2003-12-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20031223194256/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/1407543.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|ITV數位|ITV Digital}}的失敗導致格拉納達和卡爾頓損失超過10億英鎊<ref name="billion">{{Cite news |title=ITV Digital put into liquidation |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/2340335.stm |work=BBC |date=2002-10-18 |access-date=2011-07-06 |archive-date=2008-03-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080305052941/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/2340335.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，在2001年至2003年降低了公司的價值<ref>{{Cite news |title=No coronation for Granada |quote=In the case of Granada, the company's value has fallen by a quarter in the space of a month. |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2000/sep/27/business.city?INTCMP=SRCH |date=2000-09-27 |access-date=2011-07-03 |work=The Guardian |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925200957/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2000/sep/27/business.city?INTCMP=SRCH |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
===ITV格拉納達和ITV各公司的統一===
2002年10月28日，格拉納達更名為ITV1格拉納達。和其它ITV業者類似，格拉納達不再以獨自名義播出節目<ref>{{Cite news |title=Name dropping signals end of an era for Granada |last=Tryhorn |first=Chris |url=https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2003/oct/08/christryhorn |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2003-10-08 |access-date=2011-08-01 |archive-date=2020-09-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200929214411/https://www.theguardian.com/uk/2003/oct/08/christryhorn |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

在獲得政府同意後，格拉納達和卡爾頓合併<ref>{{Cite news |title=ITV cleared for a united kingdom |last=Litterick |first=David |url=https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/2865417/ITV-cleared-for-a-united-kingdom.html |newspaper=The Daily Telegraph |location=London |date=2003-10-08 |access-date=2011-06-26 |archive-date=2020-09-22 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200922215743/https://www.telegraph.co.uk/finance/2865417/ITV-cleared-for-a-united-kingdom.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2004年2月2日，兩家公司共組[[獨立電視公司|獨立電視公司]]<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada gobbles up caterer |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/752338.stm |work=BBC |date=2000-05-17 |access-date=2011-08-05 |archive-date=2004-05-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040526082604/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/752338.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。格拉納達擁有新公司68%的股份，卡爾頓擁有32%。獨立電視公司侯任董事長[[迈克尔·菲利普·格林|迈克尔·菲利普·格林]]被股東罷免<ref>{{Cite news |title=Carlton accepts defeat in ITV row |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/3209658.stm |work=BBC News |date=2003-10-21 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2006-03-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20060314110652/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/business/3209658.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>，大多數新董事會成員來自格拉納達<ref>{{Cite news |title=Proposed ITV board |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/oct/22/broadcasting.ITV2?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487 |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2003-10-22 |accessdate=2021-06-22 |archive-date=2021-02-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210225220937/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/oct/22/broadcasting.ITV2?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。卡爾頓員工被併入格拉納達業務或裁員<ref>{{Cite news |title=ITV starts its make-over |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/3090502.stm |work=BBC |date=2003-09-09 |access-date=2011-08-05 |first=Nick |last=Higham}}</ref>。四個新部門中，有三個由格拉納達員工領導<ref>{{Cite news |title=Casualties of the ITV merger |last=Higham |first=Nick |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/3286941.stm |work=BBC |date=2003-12-03 |access-date=2011-08-05}}</ref>。

2006年11月開始，除了《{{link-en|ITV新聞格拉納達報告|ITV News Granada Reports|格拉納達報告}}》之外，「格拉納達」一詞全面從電視中消失。2009年，ITV將其各部門中的格拉納達品牌刪除，格拉納達美國更名為ITV工作室美國<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada name to disappear from ITV businesses |last=Holmwood |first=Leigh |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/may/28/granada-itv |date=2009-05-28 |access-date=2011-06-30 |work=guardian.co.uk (web only) |archive-date=2021-01-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210125012616/http://www.theguardian.com/media/2009/may/28/granada-itv |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
===現在===
ITV在2009年裁員600人，實際關閉了利茲的攝影棚，並在倫敦裁撤更多崗位，但格拉納達相對受影響較輕<ref>{{Cite news |title=ITV cuts: Manchester won't be hardest hit, Countdown comes to Quay Street |url=http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-news/north-west-broadcasting/itv-cuts%3A-manchester-won%E2%80%99t-be-hardest-hit%2C-countdown-comes-to-quay-street-20090305 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111120011958/http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-news/north-west-broadcasting/itv-cuts%3A-manchester-won%E2%80%99t-be-hardest-hit,-countdown-comes-to-quay-street-20090305 |archive-date=2011-11-20 |work=how-do.co.uk |date=2009-03-05 |access-date=2011-07-28 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2009年的ITV地方新聞裁撤中，格拉納達是三個不受影響的地區之一<ref>{{Cite news |title=Seventeen regions into nine: How the updated ITV local news services will run |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/organgrinder/2009/feb/16/seventeen-regions-into-nine-itv-news |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2009-02-17 |access-date=2011-07-29 |first=Caitlin |last=Fitzsimmons |archive-date=2021-05-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210510145612/https://www.theguardian.com/media/organgrinder/2009/feb/16/seventeen-regions-into-nine-itv-news |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

按[[Ofcom|Ofcom]]的要求，ITV的節目中有50%需要在倫敦以外製作。但這一目標在2007年和2008年並未完全實現<ref>{{Cite news |title=Ofcom considers new ITV action |url=http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-news/north-west-broadcasting/ofcom-considers-new-itv-action-200805222651 |work=How-do.co.uk |date=2008-05-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120926091720/http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-news/north-west-broadcasting/ofcom-considers-new-itv-action-200805222651 |archive-date=2012-09-26 |accessdate=2021-06-22 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2013年3月25日，ITV耗資8,000萬英鎊，將其在曼徹斯特的部門遷入英國媒體城，維持曼徹斯特在北部的中心地位。

==攝影棚==
[[Image:Granada_TV.jpg|thumb]]
在獲得特許經營權至正式開播的這段時間內，格拉納達在{{link-en|碼頭街|Quay Street}}修建了新的攝影棚。該地據傳曾是墓地，但在1772年至1960年的12張地圖並無證據支持這一說法<ref>{{Cite news |title=Manchester Historical Maps |url=http://manchester.publicprofiler.org/beta/ |access-date=2011-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120204225439/http://manchester.publicprofiler.org/beta/ |archive-date=2012-02-04 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。格拉納達攝影棚比[[倫敦電視中心|BBC電視中心]]更早啟用四年，是英國第一個電視專用攝影棚<ref name="firststudio">{{Cite news |title=Granada Television |url=http://www.screenonline.org.uk/tv/id/507673/ |work=screenonline.org.uk |access-date=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2020-10-20 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201020092850/http://www.screenonline.org.uk/tv/id/507673/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。伯恩斯坦誇大了攝影棚的規模，讓格拉納達看起來足以匹敵BBC，他僅給攝影棚進行偶數編號，令其看起來有12個攝影棚，但實際上僅有6個<ref name="media">{{Cite news |title=3SixtyMedia: The North's Production Facility |url=http://www.the-manchester-studios.tv/ |work=3SixtyMedia |access-date=2011-07-04 |archive-date=2014-03-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140331091427/http://www.the-manchester-studios.tv/ |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

2010 年 9 月，位于 Quay Street 的 Granada Studios 屋顶和入口上著名的 1950 年代红色地标“Granada TV”标志在维修后发现严重腐蚀后，出于安全原因被拆除[52]。[53]有些人声称这些标志将被归还。[54]的科学与工业博物馆（MOSI）已登记在继承的迹象，认为它曼彻斯特文化遗产重要的兴趣。[55]

2010年9月，格拉納達攝影棚屋頂上的紅色「Granada TV」標誌及攝影棚在碼頭街的入口被拆除<ref>{{Cite news |title=A sign of the times ... Granada TV goes missing from Quay Street |url=http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-news/north-west-broadcasting/a-sign-of-the-times...-granada-tv-goes-missing-from-quay-street-201009279173/ |work=how-do.co.uk |date=2010-09-27 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101203113613/http://www.how-do.co.uk/north-west-media-news/north-west-broadcasting/a-sign-of-the-times...-granada-tv-goes-missing-from-quay-street-201009279173 |archive-date=2010-12-03 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。標誌在維修時發現已嚴重被腐蝕，因安全原因而不得不被拆除<ref>{{Cite news |title=Doubts over future of Granada TV sign in Manchester |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/manchester/hi/people_and_places/newsid_9040000/9040432.stm |work=BBC Manchester |date=2010-09-28 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-date=2020-11-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201106122524/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/manchester/hi/people_and_places/newsid_9040000/9040432.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。曾有消息稱這一標誌將還給格拉納達<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada TV Sign "Will Return" To Manchester Skyline |last=Watkins |first=Mike |url=http://www.atvnewsnetwork.co.uk/today/index.php/atv-today/4055-granada-tv-sign-will-return-to-manchester-skyline |work=atvnewsnetwork.co.uk |date=2010-09-27 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101002155510/http://www.atvnewsnetwork.co.uk/today/index.php/atv-today/4055-granada-tv-sign-will-return-to-manchester-skyline |archive-date=2010-10-02 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但[[科學產業博物館|科學產業博物館]]亦有意收藏這一標誌，認為其是曼徹斯特文化遺產的重要象徵<ref>{{Cite news |title=MOSI offers new home for iconic Granada TV sign |last=McKeegan |first=Alice |url=http://menmedia.co.uk/manchestereveningnews/news/s/1344384_mosi_offers_new_home_for_iconic_granada_tv_sign |newspaper=Manchester Evening News |date=2010-10-05 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-date=2010-12-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101210041658/http://menmedia.co.uk/manchestereveningnews/news/s/1344384_mosi_offers_new_home_for_iconic_granada_tv_sign |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

===搬遷===
在2004年ITV合併之後，ITV曾考慮出售碼頭街的攝影棚，員工、攝影棚、辦公區均搬進了附近的大廈。ITV預計BBC將買下這片土地，但BBC決定搬至位於{{link-en|索爾福德碼頭|Salford Quays}}的[[英國媒體城|英國媒體城]]。ITV則考慮搬遷至英國媒體城對面的{{link-en|曼徹斯特船舶運河|Manchester Ship Canal}}特拉福德碼頭（Trafford Wharf），並在2008年達成原則性協議<ref>{{Cite news |title=ITV closes in on MediaCity move |last=Rooth |first=Ben |url=http://menmedia.co.uk/manchestereveningnews/news/business/s/1065927_itv_closes_in_on_mediacity_move |newspaper=Manchester Evening News |date=2008-09-09 |access-date=2011-10-17 |archive-date=2010-08-31 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100831070014/http://menmedia.co.uk/manchestereveningnews/news/business/s/1065927_itv_closes_in_on_mediacity_move |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2009年3月，在經濟蕭條之中，格拉納達宣布將留在碼頭街<ref>{{cite news |url= http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/broadcasting/a149299/corrie-to-stay-on-quay-street.html |title= 'Corrie' to stay on Quay Street |date= 2009-03-11 |first= James |last= Welsh |work= Digital Spy |accessdate= 2021-06-22 |archive-date= 2009-06-10 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20090610064257/http://www.digitalspy.co.uk/broadcasting/a149299/corrie-to-stay-on-quay-street.html |dead-url= no }}</ref>。但遭管理層變動後，談判在2010年1月重新開始<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2010/jan/11/coronation-street-set-to-be-demolished |title=''Coronation Street'' set to be demolished |work=guardian.co.uk (web only) |date=2010-01-11 |author=Conlan, Tara |accessdate=2021-06-22 |archive-date=2020-10-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023032926/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2010/jan/11/coronation-street-set-to-be-demolished |dead-url=no }}</ref>。兩年後的2010年12月16日，格拉納達宣布將和[[索爾福德大學|索爾福德大學]]一同遷入英國媒體城的橙色大樓，並計劃在特拉福德碼頭修建攝影棚，用來拍攝ITV旗艦肥皂劇《加冕街》。工程在2011年9月6日開始施工<ref name="BBC News start construction">{{cite news|title=Work starts on new ''Coronation Street'' studio in Salford|url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-manchester-14810914|access-date=2011-09-07|newspaper=BBC News|date=2011-09-06|archive-date=2015-09-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150926003235/http://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-manchester-14810914|dead-url=no}}</ref>，計劃在2012年竣工<ref>{{cite press release | url = http://www.itvplc.com/media/newsrelease/?id=40944 | publisher = ITV | title = ITV agrees move to MediaCityUK | date = 2010-12-16 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20110723003912/http://www.itvplc.com/media/newsrelease/?id=40944 | archive-date = 2011-07-23 | access-date = 2021-06-22 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。ITV格拉納達在2013年3月25日遷入英國媒體城。

==節目==
[[File:Rovers_Return_tour.jpg|thumb]]》的拍攝現場 ]]
1958年，格拉納達報道了{{link-en|1958年羅奇代爾補選|1958 Rochdale by-election}}，這是英國電視業第一次報道選舉<ref>{{Cite news |title=Manchester on TV: Ghosts of Winter Hill |url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/manchester/hi/people_and_places/arts_and_culture/newsid_8332000/8332589.stm |work=BBC |date=2009-10-30 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-date=2019-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101152506/http://news.bbc.co.uk/local/manchester/hi/people_and_places/arts_and_culture/newsid_8332000/8332589.stm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。同時格拉納達還播出了兩場候選人辯論<ref>{{Cite news |title=The 1950s – TV election – yet another first for pioneering town |url=http://menmedia.co.uk/rochdaleobserver/news/s/333158_the_1950s |newspaper=Manchester Evening News |date=2003-06-11 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-date=2012-11-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121112192146/http://menmedia.co.uk/rochdaleobserver/news/s/333158_the_1950s |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

格拉納達在紀錄片領域上有很高成就。例如1964年開始播出的《[[成長系列|成長系列]]》是一項社會實驗，追踪14名7歲英國兒童的人生。該節目每隔7年追踪一次觀察對象的人生，觀察他們的希望和抱負是否實現。這部紀錄片被譽為史上最佳紀錄片之一，最新一期在2019年播出。《[[成長系列|成長系列]]》曾是紀錄片節目《{{link-en|世界在行動|World in Action}}》（在1963年至1998年播出）的一部分。該節目雖然獲獎，但亦引發爭議。《世界在行動》是一檔硬派的調查報道節目，其製作人{{link-en|格斯·麥克唐納|Gus Macdonald}}稱該節目「生來傲慢」<ref name="worldin">{{Cite news |title=World in Action – British news documentary |last=Jones |first=Judith |url=http://www.museum.tv/eotvsection.php?entrycode=worldinacti |access-date=2011-07-01 |archive-date=2013-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130514045925/http://www.museum.tv/eotvsection.php?entrycode=worldinacti |dead-url=no }}</ref>。{{link-en|保羅·格林格拉斯|Paul Greengrass}}稱{{link-en|大衛·普勞萊特|David Plowright}}告訴他「不要忘記，你的工作是製造麻煩」<ref name="maketrouble">{{Cite news |title=A whirlwind in action |last=Armstrong |first=Stephen |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/jun/09/itv.television |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2008-06-09 |access-date=2011-07-01 |archive-date=2021-03-08 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210308222434/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2008/jun/09/itv.television |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 《世界在行動》揭露了1985年[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]弊案、1991年皇室家庭漏稅等問題<ref name="worldin"/>，並在1985年掀起一場運動以證明{{link-en|伯明翰六人組|Birmingham Six}}的清白<ref>{{Cite news |title=Birmingham Six release remembered |last=Lissaman |first=Clare |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-12664938 |work=BBC |date=2011-03-14 |access-date=2011-07-04 |archive-date=2021-05-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210516183304/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/uk-england-12664938 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《[[加冕街|加冕街]]》是一部經典的描寫北方勞工階級的肥皂劇，開播於1960年12月9日，最初計劃播出13週，但現已成為世界播出時間最長的肥皂劇，現在仍在播出<ref>{{Cite news |title=Coronation Street goes into anti-leak lockdown |last=Youngs |first=Ian |url=https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11409278 |work=BBC News |date=2010-09-24 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2021-06-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210609072048/https://www.bbc.co.uk/news/entertainment-arts-11409278 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。此外格拉納達還製作過《[[歇洛克·福尔摩斯_(1984年电视剧)|福爾摩斯探案]]》、《{{link-en|皇冠上的寶石|The Jewel in the Crown (TV series)}}》、《[[故園風雨後|故園風雨後]]》等電視劇。

長壽競猜節目亦是格拉納達的招牌節目。《{{link-en|大學挑戰|University Challenge}}》播出於1962年至1987年，並在1994年由BBC再次播出（但由格拉納達製作）。播出於1977年至1995年的《{{link-en|報紙說什麼|What the Papers Say}}》是格拉納達最長壽的節目之一，自1956年開始播出<ref>{{Cite news |title=What The Papers Say: 50 years |last=Brockman |first=David |url=http://www.transdiffusion.org/emc/behindthescreens/what_the_papers.php |work=transdiffusion.org |year=2006 |access-date=2011-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110608124944/http://www.transdiffusion.org/emc/behindthescreens/what_the_papers.php |archive-date=2011-06-08 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==評價==
===獎項和榮譽===
格拉納達以其強大的節目製作能力而著稱<ref>{{cite web |title=Top 10 ITV companies | 1 – Granada |url=http://www.transdiffusion.org/tmc/itv50/companies/01.php |publisher=transdiffusion.org |date=2008-01-29 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110609070457/http://www.transdiffusion.org/tmc/itv50/companies/01.php |archive-date=2011-06-09 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Producers shun fight for ITV crown |last=Milmo |first=Dan |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/oct/21/citynews.itv1 |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2003-10-21 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926192049/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/oct/21/citynews.itv1 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。1999年，ITV收視率最高的八個節目都是由格拉納達製作；英國收視率最高的節目中，有30%由格拉納達製作<ref name="andthen"></ref>。2005年，ITV原創節目中有63%由格拉納達製作<ref name="MediaGuardian">{{Cite news |title=Allen denies Granada will turn in-house |last=Brown |first=Maggie |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2005/sep/14/broadcasting.ITV1?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487 |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2005-09-14 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925205426/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2005/sep/14/broadcasting.ITV1?INTCMP=ILCNETTXT3487 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在1954年自ITA獲得獨立電視特許經營權的業者中，格拉納達是唯一存在至今的業者<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada close to ITV coup |last=Teather |first=David |url=https://www.theguardian.com/business/2000/jul/28/towardsasingleitv.itv |newspaper=The Guardian |location=London |date=2000-07-28 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2020-09-26 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200926193834/https://www.theguardian.com/business/2000/jul/28/towardsasingleitv.itv |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====對曼徹斯特中心的批評====
在其經歷過的三次特許經營權競標中，競爭對手都提出了比格拉納達更高的價格，但因格拉納達廣受尊敬而未能取代格拉納達<ref>{{cite web|last=Rogers|first=Jeremy|title=Granada History|url=http://www.users.zetnet.co.uk/itw/Granada/history.html|access-date=2013-08-14|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126011000/http://www.users.zetnet.co.uk/itw/Granada/history.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。競爭對手聲稱格拉納達過於曼徹斯特中心，忽視了利物浦地區，並需要顧及整個全西北英格蘭<ref name="granadamanchester">{{Cite news |title=Granada Manchester ups sticks |url=http://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/multi-platform/news/granada-manchester-ups-sticks/1130048.article |work=broadcastnow.com |date=2003-11-19 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2020-09-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200918203552/https://www.broadcastnow.co.uk/news/multi-platform/news/granada-manchester-ups-sticks/1130048.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>。格拉納達的大多數節目在曼徹斯特製作，而2005年格拉納達和{{link-en|曼徹斯特市議會|Manchester City Council}}共同慶祝其開播50週年進一步加強了其曼徹斯特中心的看法<ref>{{Cite news |title=Manchester City Council and ITV Granada celebrate ITV@ 50 |url=http://www.manchester.gov.uk/news/article/784/manchester_city_council_and_itv_granada_celebrate_itv_50 |work=manchester.gov.uk |date=2005-10-05 |access-date=2011-07-30 |archive-date=2012-10-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121005090357/http://www.manchester.gov.uk/news/article/784/manchester_city_council_and_itv_granada_celebrate_itv_50 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Letter: The quality films that Granada has promised but failed to deliver |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/letter-the-quality-films-that-granada-has-promised-but-failed-to-deliver-1495832.html |newspaper=The Independent |location=London |date=1993-03-06 |access-date=2011-06-23 |archive-date=2012-08-03 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120803094418/http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/letter-the-quality-films-that-granada-has-promised-but-failed-to-deliver-1495832.html }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=Letter: Granada's strength in Liverpool |last=Liddiment |first=David |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/letter-granadas-strength-in-liverpool-1496892.html |newspaper=The Independent |location=London |date=1993-03-11 |access-date=2011-06-27 |archive-date=2012-08-02 |archive-url=https://archive.today/20120802054242/http://www.independent.co.uk/opinion/letter-granadas-strength-in-liverpool-1496892.html }}</ref>。

格拉納達增加了其對利物浦的投資，在1986年將其地方新聞節目製作搬至[[阿爾伯特碼頭|阿爾伯特碼頭]]<ref>{{Cite news |title=Granada Television |url=http://www2.tv-ark.org.uk/itvnorthwest/granadatv/news.html |work=tv-ark.org.uk |access-date=2011-07-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120212001918/http://www2.tv-ark.org.uk/itvnorthwest/granadatv/news.html |archive-date=2012-02-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。但在2000年代早期，地方新聞又搬回碼頭街製作。格拉納達在上午播出的節目《{{link-en|今晨 (電視節目)|This Morning (TV programme)|今晨}}》曾長期在利物浦阿爾伯特碼頭製作，但在1996年因難以邀請名人從倫敦至利物浦製作節目為由而搬遷至[[倫敦攝影棚|倫敦攝影棚]]製作<ref>{{Cite news |title=Opinion: Alex Connock |url=http://menmedia.co.uk/manchestereveningnews/comment/blogs/s/1301990_opinion_alex_connock |newspaper=Manchester Evening News |date=16 July 2010 |access-date=29 July 2011 |archive-date=2011-07-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110719145248/http://menmedia.co.uk/manchestereveningnews/comment/blogs/s/1301990_opinion_alex_connock |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

====對《世界在行動》和《今夜》的批評====
格拉納達大膽的紀錄片為其製造了眾多法律案件<ref name="maketrouble"/>。1998年，格拉納達在兩起案件中賠償200萬英鎊，分別是錯誤指控三名[[倫敦警察廳|倫敦警察廳]]警察涉嫌隱瞞謀殺案<ref>{{Cite news |title=World in Action's pounds 2m libel pay-out |last=Sanai |first=Darius |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/world-in-actions-pounds-2m-libel-payout-1201073.html |newspaper=The Independent |date=1998-09-28 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-date=2015-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150925203836/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world-in-actions-pounds-2m-libel-payout-1201073.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>；以及聲稱[[馬莎百貨|馬莎百貨]]坐視其供應商使用童工<ref>{{Cite news |title=M&S victory over child labour libel |last=Brown |first=Rob |url=https://www.independent.co.uk/news/ms-victory-over-child-labour-libel-1148172.html |newspaper=The Independent |date=1998-03-04 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-date=2019-11-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191101181548/https://www.independent.co.uk/news/ms-victory-over-child-labour-libel-1148172.html |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=M&S defeats Granada in TV libel case |url=http://www.marketingweek.co.uk/home/ms-defeats-granada-in-tv-libel-case/2022305.article |work=marketingweek.co.uk |date=1998-03-05 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-date=2012-10-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121010112737/http://www.marketingweek.co.uk/home/ms-defeats-granada-in-tv-libel-case/2022305.article |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

《世界在行動》在1998年被停播，且被《{{link-en|今夜 (1999年電視節目)|Tonight (1999 TV programme)|今夜}}》節目取代。該節目雖然有被認為不夠硬派的批評，但同樣引起批評。該節目在2003年播出的紀錄片《[[Living_with_Michael_Jackson|Living with Michael Jackson]]》被[[迈克尔·杰克逊|迈克尔·杰克逊]]威脅將發起法律訴訟<ref>{{Cite news |title=Jackson takes action against Granada over interview |last=Pyke |first=Nicholas |url=https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/feb/25/michaeljacksontrial.arts |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2003-02-25 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-date=2020-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200925192250/https://www.theguardian.com/media/2003/feb/25/michaeljacksontrial.arts |dead-url=no }}</ref>。《Living with Michael Jackson》在英國有1,500萬觀眾收看，報紙稱傑克遜在這部紀錄片被負面描寫<ref>{{Cite news |title=I was betrayed by Bashir, rages Jackson |last=Branigan |first=Tania |url=https://www.theguardian.com/news/2003/feb/07/uknews |newspaper=The Guardian |date=2003-02-07 |access-date=2011-07-05 |archive-date=2021-05-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210524083919/https://www.theguardian.com/news/2003/feb/07/uknews |dead-url=no }}</ref>。傑克遜最後並未提起訴訟。

